	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc vesperi, compater in domino charissime, a charissimo fratre et compatre meo d. <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallero</persName> accepi, quod ad dominum questorem <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8012" cert="high">Sulpicium Hallerum</persName> et ad antesignanum <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8389">Hagium</persName> de augendo mihi salario scripseris.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habeo ob hanc tibi humanitatem iam aliquoties in hac causa declaratam, quas possum maximas gratias.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Psalterium meum nuncupavi reipublicę isti; ubi illud absolutum dabitur, erit forsan occasio hac de re aliquid agendi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domus mea peste laborat iam duas septimanas.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20957" cert="high">Sara</persName> mea 20. huius mensis obdormivit in domino.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName cert="high" type="citizen_name">Nicolaus</persName>, nepos ex fratre, quintadecima laborare coepit peste, sed per gratiam domini convaluit; consimiliter et <persName type="citizen_name">Ester</persName> 22. mane peste correpta adhuc cum carbunculis, quos in sinistra coxendice quatuor habet, conflictatur; spes tamen est evasuram gratia domini.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quę ad me per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l882" cert="high">Hungaros</placeName> sunt scripta, hic mitto.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rogarunt amici quidam ex <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustanis</placeName>, ut publicarem.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mirabilis est cursus verbi dei.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Det dominus, ne illo privemur.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303" cert="high">Magdeburgensibus</placeName> ipse scis, quomodo sint obsidione cincti.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polonię</placeName> duas cohortes militum nihil obstante obsidione intromisit; deinde cives eruperunt in monasterium quoddam, ubi capitanei hostium convivaturi et genio habenas daturi erant et cunctos occiderunt.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec ad me <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2916" cert="high">Schertlinus</persName>.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Optime vale, compater in domino charissime.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutem tuis omnibus, dominis etiam et fratribus d. <persName ref="p8171" cert="high">Theodoro</persName>, <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicano</persName>, <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gvalthero</persName>.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName> 28. novembris 1550.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8417" cert="high">W[olfgangus] Musc[ulus]</persName>, compater tuus in domino.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Excellenti theologo m. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinae</placeName> ecclesiae antistiti vigilantissimo, d. et compatri suo longe charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
